This is my vim configuration. I do not suggest using it right now, cause I still need to clean up stuff a lot.

Here are the installation instructions I copied from https://raw.github.com/nelstrom/dotvim/master/README :

Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/svelix/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlink:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
